# Changelog

## [0.1.2] - 2026-03-16
### LangChain compatibility update
- Updated `robust_invoke` imports to support newer LangChain versions
- Replaced deprecated `langchain.schema.OutputParserException` with `langchain_core.exceptions.OutputParserException`
- Replaced `pydantic.v1.ValidationError` import with `pydantic.ValidationError`

## [0.1.1] - 2025-09-09
### Project link fixes
- Fixed project links in the documentation
- Updated README with correct URLs

## [0.1.0] - 2025-09-08
### Initial public release
- First version of the library

## [0.0.3] - 2025-07-24
### Proper library structure
- Restructured the library layout for better organization
- Improved module imports and exports

## [0.0.2] - 2025-07-23
### Examples tuned and file cleanup
- Updated examples to better reflect usage
- Removed unused files and directories

## [0.0.1] - 2025-06-30
